    <!-- Instructions + PDF actions -->
    <string name="instr_title">Instructions (summary)</string>
    <string name="instr_body">
Print the A4 guide at 100% (75 mm circle). Check that the reference bar (50 mm) is to scale. Place the Demolens inside the circle and take the photo. The app will use that reference to trace the shape. It is very important to use indirect lighting and avoid reflections. Lights or shadows on the Demolens prevent proper tracing. Check the visible information against the Demolens to verify the measurements and, if necessary, correct the horizontal orientation using the axis adjustment slider.
    </string>

